{
  "id": "svg-gooey-filter",
  "title": "SVG Gooey Filter",
  "summary": "Blobs that merge with a liquid 'metaball' connection using an SVG blur + contrast filter.",
  "description": "The classic gooey effect: feGaussianBlur softens shapes, then feColorMatrix cranks alpha contrast so overlapping blurred edges snap together into a liquid blob. Applied to CSS-animated circles.",
