  "dependencies": [],
  "browser_support": "All modern browsers. The filter can be defined in a 0-size inline SVG and referenced from CSS via filter: url(#goo).",
  "performance_notes": "SVG blur filters are moderately expensive; keep the filtered area small and the element count low. Motion is CSS transform (cheap).",
  "accessibility_notes": "Purely decorative; blob motion stops under prefers-reduced-motion. The contrast matrix can produce hard edges — keep it off text.",
